{"tid":872751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平南下廣東視察格力電器 強調自主創新","createTime":"2018-10-23T02:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T13:24:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a418c68bf59f3fb74340106f744eca887c7226d","tid":872751,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"新華社23日報導，22日下午，中共中央總書記、大陸國家主席習近平來到廣東省珠海市格力電器公司，先後視察公司展廳、精密模具車間和重點實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，從大國到強國，實體經濟發展至關重要，任何時候都不能「脫實向虛」。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，製造業是實體經濟的一個關鍵，製造業的核心就是創新，就是掌握關鍵核心技術，必須靠自力更生奮鬥，靠自主創新爭取，希望所有企業都朝著這個方向去奮鬥。我們要有自主創新的骨氣和志氣，加快增強自主創新能力和實力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181023001583-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181023001583-260409&d=xxb5AzGlMsE1Na28VbEcx%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1e94f6e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181023001583-260409</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n格力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2069258e22b9988f5724b2895210eae1b41a8f2a","tid":872751,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e6/Yi_Gang_Wei_Gang_Quan_Mian_Yue_Jin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe6%2FYi_Gang_Wei_Gang_Quan_Mian_Yue_Jin.jpg&h=7b2e9cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5081a1bf9039888b93bbc874fea17ce2ce69727","tid":872751,"uid":30686,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"共產中文睇到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448be3c9540249adc8159be872a10a3e73764490","tid":872751,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"自主創新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face